1122
00:57:49.581 --> 00:57:50.749
I am the director

1123
00:57:50.833 --> 00:57:52.418
of the New England
Book Association.


1124
00:57:52.501 --> 00:57:55.004
Hi, Carl. I know who you are.

1125
00:57:55.087 --> 00:57:57.339
<i>Oh, good.
Then perhaps you'll also know</i>


1126
00:57:57.423 --> 00:57:59.425
that each year
my organization bestows


