1129
00:58:06.223 --> 00:58:08.100
Especially those of us
who haven't won it.


1130
00:58:08.183 --> 00:58:11.228
Yeah. Yeah.

1131
00:58:11.312 --> 00:58:13.897
Well, that's sort of related
to why I'm calling.


1132
00:58:13.981 --> 00:58:15.524
Like many
American institutions,


1133
00:58:15.607 --> 00:58:17.359
