1171
00:59:49.451 --> 00:59:51.036
And we thought
it might be nice


1172
00:59:51.120 --> 00:59:52.621
to visit a museum.

1173
00:59:52.704 --> 00:59:54.415
Yes, of course.

1174
00:59:54.498 --> 00:59:56.500
I'm free today,
so I can look after Mother.


1175
01:00:01.922 --> 01:00:02.923
Lorraine.

1176
