1212
01:01:31.178 --> 01:01:32.304
-  You?
- Yeah, the real me.


1213
01:01:32.387 --> 01:01:34.556
Monk, you're not that famous.

1214
01:01:34.640 --> 01:01:36.058
And nobody in Hollywood reads.

1215
01:01:36.141 --> 01:01:37.851
They got their assistants
