01:03:00.350 --> 01:03:02.394
Well, what's funny?

1240
01:03:02.477 --> 01:03:04.271
Ah, it's just a strange order
for a guy like you.


1241
01:03:05.063 --> 01:03:06.565
Why is that?

1242
01:03:06.648 --> 01:03:08.942
Well, you don't see many
convicts drinking white wine.


1243
01:03:09.818 --> 01:03:11.987
You know many convicts?

1244
01:03:12.070 --> 01:03:13.196
You'd be surprised.

1245
01:03:13.280 --> 01:03:15.699
I spent a month
in the joint myself.


1246
01:03:15.782 --> 01:03:17.075
It was some interstate
commerce shit.


1247
01:03:17.159 --> 01:03:18.493
