you might be a phony.


1260
01:03:49.232 --> 01:03:50.692
A lot of fakes in Hollywood.

1261
01:03:50.776 --> 01:03:52.194
Well, I'm not from Hollywood.

1262
01:03:52.277 --> 01:03:53.612
Yeah, yeah, no.
That's obvious.


1263
01:03:53.695 --> 01:03:54.988
That's obvious.

1264
01:03:55.072 --> 01:03:57.240
