with real-world pathos.


1276
01:04:19.596 --> 01:04:21.139
It kind of elevates things.

1277
01:04:21.223 --> 01:04:22.391
You might be interested
in this one


1278
01:04:22.474 --> 01:04:23.558
we're about to shoot actually.

1279
01:04:24.476 --> 01:04:26.269
It's about this white couple.

1280
01:04:26.353 --> 01:04:29.064
They get married on an old
plantation in Louisiana.


1281
01:04:29.147 --> 01:04:30.816
Then all the slave ghosts
come back,


1282
01:04:30.899 --> 01:04:31.983
