1283
01:04:32.067 --> 01:04:34.027
- Dear God.
-  I know. I know.


1284
01:04:34.111 --> 01:04:35.529
- It's great, right?

1285
01:04:35.612 --> 01:04:37.197
It's called
<i>Plantation Annihilation.</i>


1286
01:04:37.280 --> 01:04:39.491
Ryan Reynolds is going
to get decapitated


1287
01:04:39.574 --> 01:04:41.618
